---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer id="kontakt">
	<div class="footer-content">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Kontakt</p>
			<h3>La oss ta en prat</h3>
			<p class="lede">
				Enten du trenger hjelp med en proof-of-concept på edge, en trygg lansering eller en
				prat om plattformvalg – send gjerne en melding.
			</p>
			<div class="contact-chips">
				<a class="chip" href="mailto:hei@kjoshagen.online">hei@kjoshagen.online</a>
				<a class="chip" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kjoshagen" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
					>LinkedIn</a
				>
				<a class="chip" href="https://github.com/kjoshagen" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<p class="copyright">
			&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Kristian Jøshagen · kjoshagen.online
		</p>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 3em 1em 5em 1em;
		background: linear-gradient(var(--gray-gradient)) no-repeat;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
	}
	.footer-content {
		width: 1080px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1.25em;
	}
	.eyebrow {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		font-size: 0.8em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		margin: 0 0 0.2em 0;
	}
	h3 {
		margin: 0 0 0.2em 0;
	}
	.lede {
		margin: 0 0 0.75em 0;
		max-width: 680px;
	}
	.contact-chips {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.75em;
	}
	.chip {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 0.55em 0.95em;
		border-radius: 999px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--gray), 35%);
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		background: white;
		box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(var(--gray), 8%);
		transition: all 160ms ease;
	}
	.chip:hover {
		border-color: rgba(var(--gray), 55%);
		color: var(--accent-dark);
		transform: translateY(-1px);
	}
	.copyright {
		margin: 0;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}
	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		footer {
			padding: 2.4em 1em 3em 1em;
		}
		.footer-content {
			max-width: 100%;
		}
	}
</style>
